Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.39,0:01:03.75,OPJ1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}どうして僕らは出逢ったんだろう？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.76,0:01:07.02,OPJ1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}数字なんかじゃ証明できない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.09,0:01:10.70,OPJ1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}どんな歴史も色褪せるような
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.75,0:01:13.13,OPJ1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}神秘のディスカバリー
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.25,0:01:16.91,OPJ1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}ピタリとハマった　天声のパスワード
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.94,0:01:20.08,OPJ1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}宇宙Levelのシンパシー
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.12,0:01:27.93,OPJ1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}創造紀元の胎動が聞こえているか…？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.04,0:01:29.51,OPJ1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}Burning through the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.57,0:01:34.29,OPJ1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}極上の未来を作り出そう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.37,0:01:41.20,OPJ1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}争鳴の空へと飴色のジェットで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.21,0:01:46.33,OPJ1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}未熟な夢積み込んだらフルスロットル
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.35,0:01:53.30,OPJ1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}翔ぼう！想いのままに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.27,0:02:03.27,OPJ1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}Touch and go, Catch the sun!
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,=================OPC=================
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.20,0:00:57.25,OPC1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}Touch and go, Catch the sun!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.39,0:01:03.75,OPC1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}为何我们相会于此？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.76,0:01:07.02,OPC1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}单纯的数字是无法证明的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.09,0:01:10.70,OPC1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}能让一切历史黯然无色的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.75,0:01:13.13,OPC1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}神秘大发现
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.25,0:01:16.91,OPC1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}恰巧合适的 启示的密码
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.94,0:01:20.08,OPC1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}那是宇宙级的交感
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.12,0:01:27.93,OPC1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}你能听见创造新纪元的胎动吗…？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.04,0:01:29.51,OPC1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}Burning through the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.57,0:01:34.29,OPC1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}创造出至高的未来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.37,0:01:41.20,OPC1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}乘上琥珀色的喷气飞机 向着争鸣的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.21,0:01:46.33,OPC1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}载满不成熟的梦想全力踩下油门
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.35,0:01:53.30,OPC1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}飞翔吧！一如所愿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.27,0:02:03.27,OPC1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}Touch and go, Catch the sun!
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,=================EDJ=================
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.76,0:22:21.69,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}立ち止まらず歩いて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.80,0:22:24.90,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}星を数えるより
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.82,0:22:30.13,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}消せない絆が光るよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.42,0:22:37.57,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}夢は走りだした僕らを導いてる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.78,0:22:41.94,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}願いを込めて描く世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.06,0:22:47.16,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}守りたい気持ちはきっと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.28,0:22:52.55,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}立ち向かう勇気くれるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.76,0:22:55.78,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}まっすぐ伝えたいから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.96,0:22:58.81,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}歌うよ　ラララ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.03,0:23:02.01,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}届けて　ラララ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.21,0:23:06.22,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\}忘れない胸の奥で輝いてる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.23,0:23:08.65,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}君がくれた光
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.71,0:23:11.66,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}一緒に　ラララ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.69,0:23:14.63,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}願うよ　ラララ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.85,0:23:18.66,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}強く握りしめる手は暖かく
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.81,0:23:24.11,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}このままずっと離さないよ
Comment: 0,0:00:00.22,0:00:00.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,=================EDC=================
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.76,0:22:21.69,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}一意向前
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.80,0:22:24.90,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}不必计数天上星星
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.82,0:22:30.13,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}永不消失的羁绊正在绽放光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.42,0:22:37.57,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}梦想已然起步 它指引着我们
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.78,0:22:41.94,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}倾注着梦想 描绘出这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.06,0:22:47.16,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}这份想要守护什么的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.28,0:22:52.55,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}定然会给我面对一切的勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.76,0:22:55.78,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}因为我想直白地传达给你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.96,0:22:58.81,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}唱歌吧 啦啦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.03,0:23:02.01,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}接受吧 啦啦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.21,0:23:06.22,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}在心底发光发热 永不会被忘却的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.23,0:23:08.65,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}是你给我的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.71,0:23:11.66,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}一起来 啦啦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.69,0:23:14.63,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}许愿吧 啦啦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.85,0:23:18.66,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}紧握的手儿是如此温暖
